OL,3,CClass A drugs found in drug dealers
OL,4,Cpants who was 'fidgeting awkwardly'
OL,6,FA drug dealer has been given another
OL,7,Fjail sentence after officers found a
OL,8,Fstash of class A drugs in his pants
OL,9,Fafter he was seen 'fidgeting
OL,10,Fawkwardly'.
OL,12,FDijon Brown, aged 22, was seen by
OL,13,Fofficers in Sutton in Ashfield to be
OL,14,Ffidgeting awkwardly on 28 October 2022.
OL,16,FOfficers found him in possession of
OL,17,Fdozens of wraps of heroin and crack
OL,18,Fcocaine - all secreted in a clingfilm
OL,19,Fwrap in his underwear - with a street
OL,20,Fvalue of about #2,000.
