OL,6,FHe was also found in possession of
OL,7,Fmore than #500 in cash.
OL,9,FBrown, who is currently serving a jail
OL,10,Fsentence for a similar offence
OL,11,Fcommitted in July 2023, pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fearlier this year to two counts of
OL,13,Fpossessing class A drugs with intent
OL,14,Fto supply.
OL,16,FPC Ashley Whittaker-Smith, of
OL,17,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,19,F"Brown was already known to us and was
OL,20,Fclearly acting suspiciously when he
OL,21,Fcame across him.
