OL,4,Cpants who was 'fidgeting awkwardly'
OL,6,F"Dealers often hide drugs in their
OL,7,Funderwear, and we strongly suspected
OL,8,Fthis was the case here.
OL,10,F"Our suspicions were confirmed during
OL,11,Fa search back at the station and a
OL,12,Fsignificant quantity of illegal drugs
OL,13,Fwere recovered as a result."
OL,15,FHe's been sentenced to five years in
OL,16,Fjail.
